title: What is this display font?
content:
Hi, just wondering if anyone can identify this font, much appreciated!

 ![](http://web.archive.org/web/20150415094050im_/http:/typophile.com/files/kippers_6569.jpg)
author: Meloncally

comments.content: It must be **[Boxed (Bold)](http://web.archive.org/web/20150415094050/http:/www.findmyfont.com/index.php/fonts/font-preview?fset=TipoPepel%20%2F%20%28Commercial%29&ffam=Boxed%20-%20Bold&fid=8d8468ffbc7a11086b3525951ddae702&fsize=48&text=KIPPERS%20WOULD%20HAVE%20TAKEN%20OVER%20THE%20WORLD&wrap=2)** by Josep Patau Bellart [TipoPepel, 2013]

Many thanks! And great to see it has lots of weights!  
#happy
